{"lang": "en_US", "eventid": "main_16", "eventName": "Abnormal Spectrum", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "16-9", "avgTag": "Before Operation", "storyName": "Defense of the Mad", "storyInfo": "They never truly killed the Royal Guard in the nightmares of Rankin, leader of the miners.\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_bat_act37d0d0_02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g4_miningarea_polluted", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "No... no...", "name": "Young Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_attack_heavy", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Argh!", "name": "Young Miner"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-50", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The young woman falls on the ground before your eyes, a black spear 'growing' out of her body."}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Next to her body, a man is flailing with his legs, trying to push himself away from this dangerous place."}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "M-Monster...!", "name": "Terrified Miner"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wtchkgopenftstp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_blacksmoke_01", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_8_29", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Black is closing in. Black, black, black, everything is black, except for bright-red blood. You cannot even tell if you are facing something that is living or not."}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Do not fear—not one step back!", "name": "???"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Stand up, if you still have strength—", "name": "???"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Ahh!!", "name": "Miner"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The black steps through the bodies, some of whom were miners, some of whom were guards, and some of whom were just ordinary Ursines."}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The constant screams make it very clear that, whether you turn to run or not, the spears appearing out of thin air will catch you."}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "You can only watch as the spears continue to rise from the ground, impaling body after body, threatening to blanket the entire ground."}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "—", "name": "'Emperor's Blade'"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_daggerslow", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Suddenly, the spears remove themselves from the mountain of corpses, forming a longsword in the hand of the black shadow."}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The entity raises its sword and points it toward you, speaking in an indistinguishable voice."}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g4_miningarea_polluted", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "You would die standing.", "name": "'Emperor's Blade'"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "No... I'm not going to die...", "name": "???"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "I'm not going to die here.", "name": "???"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Hope. It's a good thing.", "name": "'Emperor's Blade'"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "But futile.", "name": "'Emperor's Blade'"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_oldman_walk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1964_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "'Emperor's Blade'"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Is that...?", "name": "'Emperor's Blade'"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Rankin! We're here to help!", "name": "Soldier?"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Rankin—", "name": "Soldier?"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "You—Renat?", "name": "???"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "We're here to help!", "name": "Soldier?"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "You're here! You're here to help me! My comrades, you're here—", "name": "???"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "We'll fight side-by-side, just like old times!", "name": "???"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Just like old times!", "name": "Soldier?"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Surround him! Just like old times! One falls, another takes his place!", "name": "???"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Follow me!", "name": "???"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Fool...", "name": "'Emperor's Blade'"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "You feel the heat coming from behind you, like a burning fire that spreads all over you. It makes your blood run hot, and your eyes wide and clear. They shout your name and push you forward."}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "In the embrace of solidarity, you leap and take aim at what seems to be the thorax of the black entity—"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "And impale it."}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.2, "duration": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_audience_chaos", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.8, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleTo": 1.8, "duration": 0.4, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "66_i01", "screenadapt": "coverall", "x": 0.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.6, "yScaleFrom": 1.6, "xScaleTo": 1.5, "yScaleTo": 1.5, "duration": 10.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_piercechest", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "—Death—", "name": "???"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "—", "name": "'Emperor's Blade'"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Ha...", "name": "'Emperor's Blade'"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "There is no sound of blood dripping, no convulsion."}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Only the resistance of the blade growing lesser and lesser, until it disappears altogether."}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "66_i01", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "I see... I see...", "name": "'Emperor's Blade'"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "...Gabrielus—", "name": "'Emperor's Blade'"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "As the last syllable leaves its mouth, the uniform propped up by the shadow goes limp and stops resisting."}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "???"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "You have put an end to the monster, with courage, with determination, with heart."}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "With the support of 'friends' who never existed."}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_5_7_shining", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_atmosphere_horror", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "at"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "at", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_dim_openeye", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "*pant*... *pant*...", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "Your hands are heavy. Where are you?", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "'—He's down. He's down!'"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "...Who?", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "at", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "'Rankin, you—we, we killed—'"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "'We killed him!'"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "Killed who? Black... snow...", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "Not enough. One obstacle dead and gone, but the snow is everywhere, abominable snow...", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "The snow will not stop.", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "'Rankin? Rankin! What do we do now?'"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "'Rankin—'"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "at", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tinnitus", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_newiceforest_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.4, "yScale": 1.4, "y": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 200.0, "duration": 30.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "bg_newiceforest_2", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "duration": 0.1, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.3, "posfrom": "0,-160", "posto": "0,-160", "duration": 4.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.4, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_whitemask", "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "focusparam", "attributes": {"blur": "false", "effect": "Grayscale"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Rankin!", "name": "Soldier?"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "I am...", "name": "???"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Rankin! Rankin!", "name": "Miner"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The crowd rushes toward you like the tide. They raise you up, and they pull you back down. You have felt this sense of weightlessness before."}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "The crowd shouts, the crowd yells. Someone who should not have been here shouts your name in the deafening echoes."}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "—Rankin—", "name": "Soldier?"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_whitemask", "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "focusparam", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "You close your eyes and go back into the forest with his words. A border garrison unit, a one-way mission."}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "You are not there."}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Won...", "name": "???"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "We won.", "name": "???"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_atmosphere_horror", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "at"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "at", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "bg_newiceforest_2", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "duration": 4.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g16_smokeonblackgroud", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "As you rise and fall, you look towards the black dust in the distance, which has yet to fully disperse."}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "at", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "Black Snow"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Black smoke seeps out from every hole and gap in the uniform, like countless tiny tentacles, greedily wrapping and covering it, until it is completely hidden."}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Under the black smoke, the uniform once again takes human shape, as though—"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smokeconverge", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_8_30", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "As though he never died."}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}